metadata.name: DANCING WITH DUALITY.
metadata.description:
Shadows always have a lot to say. 
We all have our dark sides and we need to accept our shadow selves. 
Without darkness there can be no cycle of life, nothing creative can take place.  
I believe in embracing duality,  in learning to let darkness and light co-exist, as illumination. 

Bali, Indonesia 
2021 
13.8 MB
3761 × 5641
